---
title: Irish Style Lamb Stew with Champ Mash
description: We love good Irish Lamb Meatball Stew and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/irish-style-meatball-stew-3956aeb7-df51c4f9.jpg
